                stunning realities. Our skilled team designs and creates
                beautiful, functional outdoor spaces tailored to your vision.
                From lush gardens to inviting patios, we bring creativity and
                craftsmanship to every project.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a
                href="#services"
                class="bg-cafe font-semibold rounded-lg py-3 px-5 hover:bg-darker_cafe lg:hover:scale-105 transition-all"
                >Our Services</a
              >

              <a
                href="#contact"
                class="bg-cafe font-semibold rounded-lg py-3 px-5 hover:bg-darker_cafe lg:hover:scale-105 transition-all"
