      <div class="container mx-auto text-center px-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold lg:text-5xl pb-3">OUR SERVICES</h2>

        <p class="w-full md:w-[75%] lg:w-[75%] mx-auto lg:py-4">
          At <span class="font-bold">MVLandscape</span>, we offer expert
          landscaping solutions to transform your outdoor space. From creative
          design and garden maintenance to hardscaping and irrigation, our
          skilled team delivers exceptional results tailored to your vision.
          Whether you need a complete overhaul or regular care, we ensure your
          landscape is both beautiful and functional. Discover how our services
          can enhance your outdoor environment.
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-6 flex-wrap pt-5 lg:gap-4 md:gap-y-7 lg:gap-y-11">
          <Card
            title="GRASS CUTTING SERVICE"
            body="Expert grass cutting for a pristine, well-maintained lawn year-round."
            link="/services/grass-cutting"
            isService
          />
          <Card
            title="LANDSCAPE DESIGN SERVICE"
            body="Transform your outdoor space with our expert landscape design service."
            link="/services/landscape-design"
            isService
          />
          <Card
            title="PLANTING SERVICE"
            body="Enhance your garden with our professional planting service."
            link="/services/planting"
            isService
          />
          <Card
            title="TREE TRIMMING SERVICE"
            body="Professional tree trimming for healthy, beautiful, and safe trees."
            link="/services/tree-trimming"
            isService
          />
          <Card
            title="SPRINKLER INSTALLATION SERVICE"
            body="Efficient sprinkler installation for a lush, well-watered landscape."
            link="/services/sprinkler-installation"
